posts.body:
>>09f866da-d049-4e42-8fed-bbfd5a920e30
If I'm not mistaken, much (though definitely not all) of the stuff posted to Millchan can be found elsewhere.

NSJ's sets often get expunged from e-hentai because they aren't cosplay, which is the one argument for uploading anything to 0net: so that it can't be taken down, provided someone is still serving the files.

Ultimately, I don't care one way or another whether or not her sets are posted here, so if people don't want to see her sets on Millchan, I definitely won't post more of them :)

And, here's the magnet url for (most? all?) of NSJ's sets up to October 2019: magnet:?xt=urn:btih:74B8C997A4D52F488792845FB9D7A06E46C5C9AF&dn=%5bnonsummerjack%5d&tr=http%3a%2f%2fehtracker.org%2f1501951%2fannounce (stoeled from e-hentai obviously lol)
